      "writtenOn": "2020-04-30T18:07:38Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "This uses performance.now() and measures timings here. This is what the first iteration of skottie-was-perf.html did as well (but used frame numbers not clock time).\nThis was changed to use chrome tracing instead because of the reasons in https://bugs.chromium.org/p/skia/issues/detail?id\u003d9237\nYou probably do not care about this right now, but something to keep in mind if we want to ever compare this approach with other frameworks that might use SVG backend (like lottie-web).",
